snippet.title: YABI - BOOMERANG ( OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO )
snippet.description:
Artist/Performer: YABI THE G.O.A.T
Recorded at: Kadak Nepali
Prod. By: Rick Anthony
Mixed & Mastered by: Ruthlexx
Mixtape: Bommerang
Directed: Samirvision

Boomerang is a raw and emotional record that comes back harder every time just like the feelings it carries.This track dives into love, pain, and the moments you can‚Äôt escape no matter how far you run.Recorded at Kadak Nepali and mixed & mastered by Ruthlexx, Boomerang brings heavy energy with a polished sound.
This song is a part of my mixtape Boomerang, a project that reflects real stories, real emotions, and real experiences.Turn the volume up, feel the bounce, and let it hit you back.This is Boomerang.

¬© 2025 YABI THE G.O.A.T. All Rights Reserved. This music video and audio are the original work of the artist. Unauthorized copying, distribution, reuploading, or use of this content in any form without written permission is strictly prohibited.

Christopher Nolan‚Äôs next film, The Odyssey, is a mythic action epic shot across the world using brand new IMAX¬Æ film technology. The film brings Homer‚Äôs foundational saga to IMAX¬Æ film screens for the first time and opens in theaters everywhere on July 17, 2026. 

The Odyssey stars Matt Damon, Tom Holland, Anne Hathaway, Robert Pattinson and Lupita Nyong‚Äôo, with Zendaya and Charlize Theron.

The Odyssey is produced by Emma Thomas and Christopher Nolan for their company, Syncopy. The executive producer is Thomas Hayslip.

snippet.title: Yabesh Thapa - Shital | OFFICIAL VISUALIZER
snippet.description:
Shital is the second song from the album 'GhaamChhaya' and is a very emotional song for me. It talks about how love would have been different if they had more time. In the end we all turn to dust. Only if he had the power to compel gods to freeze time in place, the story would have a different outcome.

Written, Composed, Produced and Performed by Yabesh Thapa

About "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara"
"Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" is a popular Nepali folk song that originates from the Lamjung district of Nepal. It is a lively and upbeat song that is typically sung and danced to during festivals and social gatherings.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

The lyrics of the song are in the Nepali language and describe the beauty of the Lamjung district's natural scenery, including the mountains, rivers, and forests. The song also celebrates the joy and happiness of the people living in Lamjung and their culture and traditions.

The musical arrangement of "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" typically features traditional Nepali instruments such as the madal (a type of drum), tungna (a stringed instrument), and sarangi (a bowed instrument). The song has a catchy melody and rhythm that are easy to dance along to.

Over time, "Lamjung Daadaama Hawa Sarara" has become a beloved Nepali folk song that is popular across the country and is often performed by musicians and dancers at cultural events and festivals.

snippet.description:
Tried to do something different, hope you guys enjoy :)

Go get the Jack Link‚Äôs x MrBeast beef sticks right now üëâ https://bit.ly/JLMBYT1

Massive shoutout to Ish who helped co-host this video, he‚Äôs an amazing storyteller and I can‚Äôt thank him enough for his time and energy, go check him out: https://youtube.com/@ish

We had thousands of players try to join our first large scale, multi day, competition civilization event in a first come first serve basis. We accepted the first 500 boys and 500 girls who joined in chronological order on the Minecraft server when it went live. If a player broke the rules they agreed to in any way or lied on their application about any information to try and sabotage other players, they were banned by the staff who were monitoring 24/7 after an investigation, their actions were reversed and players they killed were revived, and they were replaced with the next boy or girl in line who had tried to join the server earlier in chronological order.

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday ‚Äì "The X-Men Will Return" Trailer (Timeory Concept Version)
snippet.description:
This is a fan-made AI concept created by me, inspired by Avengers: Doomsday. It is a fictional interpretation and not an official trailer/scene/clip.

üëâ Steve Rogers Teaser: https://youtu.be/-pqDaCYmAVo 
üëâ Thor begs Odin: https://youtu.be/J3yXj8-CDrI 

If you use any part of this video in your edits, please credit my channel.
Please note that reuploads of this video without permission are not allowed.

The X-Men stand on the brink of extinction. Magneto and Professor X both feel it, the end is coming.

But the real question isn‚Äôt how it ends‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs what comes after.

From the pages of the comics, the Sentinels rise once more, not as weapons of control, but as instruments of erasure. A future designed to leave nothing behind.

And beyond the machines, another shadow grows. While the world watches the Sentinels, Doctor Doom prepares his own endgame.

Extinction was never the final threat. What follows it might be worse.

#AvengersDoomsday #XMen #Magneto #Cyclops #ProfessorX #DoomsdayTrailer #Marvel

*English Translation*
The fate of this weary soul is truly unfortunate,
The fate of this troubled heart is unfortunate.
Love was never written in my destiny,
Oh, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,
Indeed, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate.

A heart slashed by sharp, bitter words,
No cure is found- it keeps aching endlessly.
Wherever I go, I earn no respect,
When my own fate is flawed, whom can I blame?
Oh, the fate of this poor soul is unfortunate,
The fate of this poor soul is unfortunate.
Love was never written in my destiny,
Oh, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,
Indeed, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate.

This helpless life keeps giving me pain,
Even the little laughter I find takes away.

snippet.title: Shinchan and Franklin  Celebrate Christmas with Santa Claus in GTA 5
snippet.description:
In this video Shinchan and Franklin  Celebrate Christmas with Santa Claus in GTA 5

In this fun and festive GTA 5 story mod, Franklin transforms his house into a Christmas wonderland, decorating it with sparkling lights and a massive Christmas tree. üåü

Franklin wants to spread joy to all his gang members, so he goes on a gift-hunting adventure! First, he surprises Shinchan with an amazing 3-wheeled blue bike, then grabs a super muscle car equipped with an RPG rocket launcher! üöóüí• But the holiday fun doesn‚Äôt stop there ‚Äî Franklin also buys delicious cake and wine for everyone in the gang. üéÇüç∑

Things get magical when Franklin meets Santa Claus on his rooftop! üéÖ Santa tells him about his second sleigh, parked near the Los Santos Dam Observatory. Franklin sets off on a mission to find this beautiful sleigh and bring it home.

Finally, it‚Äôs time for the big celebration! Franklin wakes up the gang, hands out all the gifts, and invites Chop and Shinchan for a thrilling ride on the sleigh. Together, they soar across the Los Santos skyline, enjoying the festive spirit and the joy of friendship. ‚ú®

Don‚Äôt miss this epic Christmas story full of laughter, surprises, and GTA 5 chaos!

üéÅ If you enjoyed the video, hit LIKE üëç, SUBSCRIBE üîî, and share it with your friends to spread the Christmas cheer!

snippet.title: She & Him - I Thought I Saw Your Face Today (Official Lyric Video)
snippet.description:
The official lyric video for "I Thought I Saw Your Face Today" by She & Him

Subscribe To She & Him on YouTube: 
https://www.youtube.com/@SheandHimOfficial?sub_confirmation=1

Follow She & Him: 
http://www.sheandhim.com
http://www.instagram.com/sheandhim
http://www.facebook.com/sheandhim
http://www.twitter.com/sheandhim

Stream on Spotify:  https://bit.ly/ITISYFTSpotify
Stream on Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/song/i-thought-i-saw-your-face-today/1839131590
Stream on YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/ITISYFTYTMusic

Lyrics: 
I thought I saw your face today
But I just turned my head away
Your face against the trees
But I just see the memories
As they come, as they come

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again

I saw it glitter as I grew
And loved it, boy, I never knew
I thought this place was heaven-sent
But now it's just a monument
In my mind, in my mind

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again

The cars and freeways implore me to stay away, out of this place
My mother said, "Just keep your head, and play it as it lays"
The cars and freeways implore me to stay away, out of this place
My mother said, "Just keep your head, and play it as it lays"

I somehow see what's beautiful
In things that are ephemeral
I'm my only friend of mine
And love is just a piece of time
In the world, in the world

And I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall in love again
No, I couldn't help but fall...

#SheAndHim #IThoughtISawYourFaceToday

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

Unstable SMP:

minor spoilers below

featuring: @LettuceK @JadenMAN 

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!) 

orbital cannon designed by: https://www.youtube.com/@cubicmetre (the cannon used in the video is his v6 design, however the actual cannon functions very differently from how it does in this video so please be aware of that)
spear mod used: https://modrinth.com/mod/accurate-spears/versions

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, official enderal soundtrack, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)
